videos.description: South Carolina pulls out the flea-flicker and Ryan Hilinski throws it up to Bryan Edwards for the 41-yard play.
videos.headline: South Carolina gains 41 on flea-flicker

videos.description: Mon Denson lowers his shoulder and walks into the end zone for the one-yard touchdown run to open the scoring for South Carolina.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Denson pounds it in for the South Carolina TD) 2019/10/19

videos.headline: Denson pounds it in for the South Carolina TD

videos.description: Kyle Trask lofts it to Jacob Copeland, who breaks a tackle and goes 37 yards for the Gators' touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Copeland wins jump ball for Florida TD) 2019/10/19

videos.headline: Copeland wins jump ball for Florida TD

videos.description: Florida's second play of the second half is a Kyle Trask interception to Jammie Robinson.
videos.headline: Trask overthrows receiver for INT

videos.description: Ryan Hilinski sells the pass, then hands it off to Tavien Feaster who carves up the Florida defense for the 21-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (South Carolina runs excellent draw play for Feaster's TD) 2019/10/19

videos.headline: South Carolina runs excellent draw play for Feaster's TD

videos.description: Florida answers South Carolina's score immediately as Dameon Pierce gets space and runs 75 yards for the Gators' touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Florida needs 1 play to respond with Pierce's 75-yard TD) 2019/10/19

videos.headline: Florida needs 1 play to respond with Pierce's 75-yard TD

videos.description: South Carolina players and fans hold up three fingers in honor of Gamecocks QB Ryan Hilinski's brother, Tyler, who died by suicide in January 2018.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Misc. (South Carolina players, fans remember Hilinski's late brother) 2019/10/19

videos.headline: South Carolina players, fans remember Hilinski's late brother

videos.description: Kyle Trask lobs it to Freddie Swain for the 25-yard touchdown, which gives the Gators a 24-20 lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Florida takes lead on Swain's diving catch) 2019/10/19

videos.headline: Florida takes lead on Swain's diving catch

videos.description: Kyle Trask makes the simple short pass to Kyle Pitts for the five-yard score to extend Florida's lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Florida increases lead with Pitts' touchdown) 2019/10/19

videos.headline: Florida increases lead with Pitts' touchdown

videos.description: Kyle Trask hits Trevon Grimes with a quick five-yard touchdown to increase Florida's lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Grimes scores on screen pass to bury South Carolina) 2019/10/19

videos.headline: Grimes scores on screen pass to bury South Carolina

videos.description: Kyle Trask throws three fourth-quarter touchdowns as Florida knocks off South Carolina 38-27.

videos.headline: Florida silences South Carolina late in exciting 2nd half

videos.description: Will Muschamp can't help but go off about the unsportsmanlike penalty he received in the fourth quarter and calls the official that gave it to him "gutless."
